SUMMARY:Sunrise Meditation (60m) - Ericka
DESCRIPTION:Instructor: Ericka Brian\nRoom: OV Lawn\nLocation: Ocotill
 o Village\nSunrise Meditation\n\nSunday\, April 5th\, May 3rd\, June 
 7th I 6am-7am\, Event Lawn\n\nBegin each month with clarity and inten
 tion. This guided sunrise meditation experience blends breathwork\, g
 entle grounding movement\, and intentional stillness to regulate the 
 nervous system and sharpen mental focus. As the sun rises\, you’ll 
 reset your energy\, refine your vision\, and align your mindset for t
 he month ahead.\nStart centered. Stay aligned.\n \nFree Members I $45
  guests\n\nFor more information\, please contact Ericka Brian | ebria
 n@dmbclubs.com\n\nPlease sign up on the Village App.
END:VEVENT
